# 03장

### 실습 - 게시판 만들기 (게시글-페이징, 댓글, 질문 / 회원가입 / 로그인 / 질문 목록 ) p.77 참고 
	- 테이블
		1) Member
			- MEMBER_ID INT PRIMARY KEY
			- USER_ID VARCHAR(50)
			- PASSWORD VARCHAR(50)
			- NAME VARCHAR(50)
			- EMAIL VARCHAR(50)
		
		2) BOARD
			- BOARD_ID INT PRIMARY KEY
			- USER_ID VARCHAR(50) FOREIGN KEY
			- TITLE VARCHAR(100)
			- CONTENT VARCHAR(1000)
			- IMAGE VARCHAR(100)
			- HIT_COUNT INT
			- CREATED_DATE (VARCHAR 12)
			
		3) BOARD_REPLY
			- REPLY_ID PRIMARY KEY
			- BOARD_ID INT FOREIGN KEY
			- 
		 
